ps://github.com/dandi/dandi-cli/issues/1033#issuecomment-1176447518 and cited above.  \n\n @jwodder - do you mean this https://github.com/psf/requests/blob/HEAD/requests/models.py#L549  or some other location?  how could we instrument in our code to discover more about the situation better?","files":null}]}